sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor HealthWorker as "Health Worker"
    participant WebPortal as "Web Portal"
    participant Registration as "Registration Service"
    participant UID as "UID Generator"
    participant CentralDB as "Central Database"

    Note over HealthWorker,CentralDB: FR4-FR6: Core Registry and UID Generation
    HealthWorker->>WebPortal: Submit registration (patient + caregiver)
    WebPortal->>WebPortal: Validate mandatory fields
    WebPortal->>Registration: POST /patients/register
    Registration->>CentralDB: Check duplicates (name, location)
    CentralDB-->>Registration: No match found
    par Generate UID and format
      Registration->>UID: Request unique ID (e.g. ETH-1001)
      UID-->>Registration: Return UID
      Registration->>Registration: Format as FHIR Patient
    end
    Registration->>CentralDB: Begin transaction
    Registration->>CentralDB: Insert caregiver entity
    Registration->>CentralDB: Insert patient entity (linked)
    Registration->>CentralDB: Commit transaction
    CentralDB-->>Registration: Success (entities linked)
    Registration->>CentralDB: Initialize empty vaccination history
    CentralDB-->>Registration: History created
    Registration-->>WebPortal: Registration successful
    WebPortal-->>HealthWorker: Display patient dashboard
